      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore without feeling like i'm suffocating. everything is just... breaking. the weather, the politics, the ecosystems. it feels like we're all just watching a slow motion car crash and there's literally nothing anyone can do to stop it. how are you even supposed to care about a future that isn't even gonna exist?",
